FBIS4-57402 "drlat095_a_94008" FBIS-LAT-94-095 Daily Report 17 May 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Cuba Vision Introduces Additional Weekday Newscast Cuba Vision Introduces Additional Weekday Newscast FL1705014894 Havana Cuba Vision Network in Spanish 0000 GMT 17 May 94 FL1705014894 Havana Cuba Vision Network Spanish BFN [Text] As of this afternoon, Cuba Vision's viewers have a new newscast, one that will allow them to learn, early on, of the most important stories that will appear on the National Television Newscast [Noticiero Nacional de Television -- NTV]. Every day, Monday through Friday at 1927 [2327 GMT], our newsroom personnel will have ready for you a summary of the main events making the news in Cuba and in the world. We will thereby inform you, quickly and directly, about the subjects that will be reported at greater length over NTV at 2000 [0000 GMT].
